}lu, L{\"u}tf{\"u} and Hazelton, Jessica L. and Herzog, Rub{\'e}n and Ikiz, Burcin and Njamnshi, Alfred Kongnyu and {Landin-Romero}, Ramon and L{\'o}pez, Mar{\'i}a Eugenia and Maito, Marcelo Adri{\'a}n and Medel, Vicente and Sep{\'u}lveda, Juan Pablo Morales and Ochoa G{\'o}mez, John Fredy and Ogbuagu, Chukwuanugo and {de Oliveira}, Maira Okada and Ozansoy, Mehmet and {Palma-Espinosa}, Javier and Hilal, Saima and Zhou, Juan Helen and Escudero, Stefanie Danielle Pi{\~n}a and Pitman, Julie Kay and Prado, Pavel and Ram{\'i}rez Gonz{\'a}lez, Diego and Reyes, Pablo and Santamar{\'i}a Garc{\'i}a, Hernando and Schr{\"o}der, Johannes and Sitt, Jacobo Diego and Soliman, Radwa Kamel and {Soto-A{\~n}ari}, Marcio and Thanissery, Nithin and Ito, Lucas Toshio and Tsuchida, Ami and Tzourio, Christophe and Y{\i}r{\i}ko{\u g}ullar{\i}, Harun and Yokoyama, Jennifer S. and Aguillon, David and Miller, Bruce and Alladi, Suvarna and Jiang, Yang and Navarro, Arcadi and Babiloni, Claudio and Huepe Artigas, David and Piguet, Olivier and Sosa, Pedro Antonio Valdes and Mostert, Cyprian M. and Tahmasian, Masoud and Li, Peng and Hu, Kun and Genon, Sarah and Stein, Dan J. and Maest{\'u}, Fernando and Pievani, Michela and Salama, Mohamed and Brodaty, Henry and Sachdev, Perminder S. and Lawlor, Brian and Eyre, Harris A. and Miranda, J. Jaime and Baez, Sandra and Tagliazucchi, Enzo and {Duran-Aniotz}, Claudia and Hernandez, Hernan and Ibanez, Agustin},
  year = 2026,
